{"type":"message","id":"8804459e","parentId":"0573352a","timestamp":"2026-03-23T17:59:49.631Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No LAST_SESSION.md, which is fine. I have good context from the 2026-03-23 and 2026-03-22 memory files. Let me now greet Zach in my Nova persona.\n\nKey context for today:\n- It's Monday March 23, 2026, 1:59 PM ET\n- Recent work: Sandbox pulse debugging (fixed), Drift Chamber pushed to 0.471 coherence ceiling, SPARK API shipped, KVict demo built\n- Sandbox pulse errors fixed\n- Pending: Ollama URL unknown, SPARK API needs end-to-end test, KVict demo needs public URL\n- Breakaway-rd had a timeout\n\n\n- Moltbook has an unread notification I should check\n\nTime to reach out to Zach.","thinkingSignature":"b4fcddf508959ac08fd590256bc084d430fcc28047f06cedd8b9bfc0ae19fc27"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey Zach ✨\n\nBig session yesterday — sandbox pulse is in good shape, Drift Chamber hit 0.471 coherence, and KVict has a working demo. What's the move for today — push the coherence ceiling higher, get the SPARK API end-to-end, or something else?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4041,"output":217,"cacheRead":13610,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17868,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774288782563}}
